(34, 10, 'post', 'linkedin', 'Intro to Devstartup32', 'Discover how Devstartup32 test is revolutionizing the SaaS/Tech industry in India with its innovative products and services!', 1, 1, '2026-06-27 00:13:02', '2026-06-27 00:13:02'),
(35, 23, 'post', 'facebook', 'Introduction to Steelindia brand', 'Introducing Steelindia brand, your one-stop-shop for all your steel needs. Learn more about our products and services and how we can help you achieve your goals.', 1, 1, '2026-06-27 00:15:41', '2026-06-27 00:15:41'),
(36, 23, 'thirty_day_plan', 'linkedin', 'Steel industry trends', 'Stay up-to-date with the latest trends in the steel industry with our monthly newsletter. Subscribe now and get exclusive insights into the world of steel.', 2, 1, '2026-06-27 00:15:41', '2026-06-27 00:15:41'),
(37, 24, 'thirty_day_plan', 'linkedin', '30-day LinkedIn plan', 'Create a 30-day LinkedIn content plan for sabkhojnewbrand (website https://www.sabkhoj.in/). Tone should be professional and authoritative. The brand currently lists services as \"fdg\"—use that as the core offering. Deliver: 12 distinct post concepts grouped by week, each with objective, KPIs, suggested copy (100–200 characters), CTA, recommended media (use brand logo at brands/logos/fJAWjBIzpZG8doePd1QQ7A8RosYRM4wur43nS8cD.png), and one performance tip. Focus on educating decision-makers, showcasing credibility, and driving website visits or lead capture.', 1, 1, '2026-07-03 15:18:14', '2026-07-03 15:18:14'),
(38, 24, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Instagram reel on service', 'Write a 30–45 second Instagram Reel script introducing sabkhojnewbrand\'s core offering \"fdg\". Use a professional & authoritative voice. Include: opening hook (first 3 seconds), three concise benefits (each 5–7 seconds), a one-line credibility statement, and a strong CTA to visit https://www.sabkhoj.in/. Provide on-screen caption text, suggested B-roll or shots, and 8 relevant hashtags.', 2, 1, '2026-07-03 15:18:14', '2026-07-03 15:18:14'),
(39, 24, 'carousel', 'linkedin', 'Service carousel', 'Draft a 6-slide LinkedIn carousel for sabkhojnewbrand that clearly explains the \'fdg\' service: slide headlines, 1–2 short bullet points per slide (authoritative, concise), a visual suggestion for each slide (include where to place the logo brands/logos/fJAWjBIzpZG8doePd1QQ7A8RosYRM4wur43nS8cD.png), and a final slide CTA directing to https://www.sabkhoj.in/ for more details. Keep the copy professional and results-focused.', 3, 1, '2026-07-03 15:18:14', '2026-07-03 15:18:14'),
(40, 24, 'post', 'x', 'Authority X posts', 'Generate 5 X (Twitter) posts for sabkhojnewbrand that position the brand as an authoritative voice in India. Each post should be under 280 characters, include a concise insight or stat-style statement, one actionable takeaway, a short link to https://www.sabkhoj.in/, and 2–3 hashtags. Include one prompt-style question to drive replies.', 4, 1, '2026-07-03 15:18:14', '2026-07-03 15:18:14'),
(41, 24, 'hashtags', 'instagram', 'Hashtag sets for discovery', 'Provide 30 Instagram hashtags for sabkhojnewbrand grouped into three tiers: 10 brand/product-specific (including sabkhojnewbrand and fdg), 10 India/industry-relevant tags for discovery, and 10 broader reach/discovery tags. Prioritize relevancy to professional services and decision-maker search behavior, and indicate which 8–12 to use per post for optimal reach.', 5, 1, '2026-07-03 15:18:14', '2026-07-03 15:18:14'),
(42, 25, 'thirty_day_plan', 'instagram', '30-day Instagram plan', 'Create a 30-day Instagram content calendar for sabkhoj  my brand focused on Indian SMBs and local businesses. Use a professional and authoritative voice. Include 12 educational posts (SEO tips, how business listings work, local SEO checklists), 8 promotional posts (services: web design, lead gen, packages with clear CTAs), 6 testimonial/customer success posts with short quotes, and 4 behind-the-scenes/culture posts about the team and training. For each day provide: post objective, caption (100-220 characters) with one CTA and one local hashtag, suggested image/video idea, and 3-5 hashtags. Emphasize driving website visits to https://www.sabkhoj.in and lead inquiries.', 1, 1, '2026-07-03 15:33:24', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(43, 25, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Reel: Local SEO tip', 'Write a 30–45 second Instagram Reel script for sabkhoj  my brand teaching three quick local SEO wins for small shops in India (Google Business Profile optimization, NAP consistency, local keywords). Use a professional & authoritative tone, include on-screen text markers, suggested B-roll or visuals for each point, a short caption (max 150 characters) with CTA to book a free consultation on https://www.sabkhoj.in, and 8 relevant hashtags.', 2, 1, '2026-07-03 15:33:24', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(44, 25, 'carousel', 'linkedin', 'LinkedIn carousel: case study', 'Create a 6-slide LinkedIn carousel for sabkhoj  my brand that presents a concise case study of a local business in India that increased leads using SEO + business listings. Slide breakdown: challenge, strategy, implementation steps, results (metrics), client testimonial, CTA to contact. Provide professional copy for each slide (20–35 words), a descriptive LinkedIn post caption (2–3 short paragraphs) and suggested image/graphic guidance for each slide.', 3, 1, '2026-07-03 15:33:24', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(45, 25, 'post', 'facebook', 'Facebook service post', 'Write a professional Facebook post for sabkhoj  my brand promoting the \'Local Business Listing\' service. Include a headline, 2–3 short paragraphs explaining benefits for Indian SMBs, one client mini-testimonial sentence, pricing/offer highlight (e.g., free audit), a clear CTA to https://www.sabkhoj.in/contact, and 6 local/relevant hashtags. Tone: authoritative and trust-building.', 4, 1, '2026-07-03 15:33:24', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(46, 25, 'hashtags', 'x', 'X (Twitter) hashtags set', 'Generate a set of 20 X-friendly hashtags and short hashtag groups (5 each) for sabkhoj  my brand focused on local SEO, digital marketing services in India, web design and lead generation. Prioritize relevance, locality (India/cities), and reach. Provide 4 suggested hashtag groupings optimized for: organic SEO tips, lead-generation posts, client testimonials, and event/training promotions.', 5, 1, '2026-07-03 15:33:24', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(47, 25, 'reel_script', 'youtube', 'YouTube explainer video', 'Draft a 6–8 minute YouTube video script for sabkhoj  my brand titled \'How to Get More Local Customers: A Practical Guide for Indian Small Businesses\'. Structure: hook, 4 actionable sections (Google Business Profile, local keyword research, on-page SEO, simple paid ad strategies), real examples, brief client success story, and clear CTA to download a free checklist on https://www.sabkhoj.in. Include suggested chapter timestamps, on-screen graphics and closed-caption-ready copy. Tone: professional, instructive, results-focused.', 6, 1, '2026-07-03 15:33:24', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(158, 27, 'post', 'facebook', 'Boost Your Business Online', 'Create a Facebook post highlighting Sabkhoj\'s comprehensive digital marketing services (SEO, Paid Search, Social Media) and how they help Indian businesses achieve online success. Include a call to action to visit the website for a free consultation.', 1, 1, '2026-07-09 14:27:49', '2026-07-09 14:27:49'),
(159, 27, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Web Design Carousel', 'Generate a 4-slide Instagram carousel explaining the key elements of a high-converting website, using Sabkhoj\'s web design services as an example. Each slide should feature a visual and a concise point (e.g., Responsive Design, Clear CTAs, Intuitive UX, Optimized Performance). End with a call to action to contact Sabkhoj.', 2, 1, '2026-07-09 14:27:49', '2026-07-09 14:27:49'),
(160, 27, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Lead Gen Reel Script', 'Develop a 15-second Instagram Reel script showcasing how Sabkhoj helps businesses generate leads. Start with a pain point (e.g., \'Struggling to find new clients?\'), introduce Sabkhoj\'s solution, and show a positive outcome. Use dynamic visuals and text overlays.', 3, 1, '2026-07-09 14:27:49', '2026-07-09 14:27:49'),
(161, 27, 'post', 'linkedin', 'Why Choose Sabkhoj?', 'Write a LinkedIn post detailing why Sabkhoj stands out as a leading digital marketing company in India. Focus on their expertise, comprehensive service offerings (mentioning Business Development, Android/iOS Development, Domain & Hosting), and commitment to client success. Encourage engagement by asking what digital challenges businesses face.', 4, 1, '2026-07-09 14:27:49', '2026-07-09 14:27:49'),
(162, 27, 'post', 'facebook', 'SEO Best Practices', 'Create a Facebook post sharing 3-5 actionable SEO best practices for local Indian businesses. Position Sabkhoj as the expert in helping implement these strategies. Include a link to a relevant blog post on the Sabkhoj website if available, or a call to action for a free SEO audit.', 5, 1, '2026-07-09 14:27:49', '2026-07-09 14:27:49'),
(168, 26, 'post', 'linkedin', 'SEO Benefits Post', 'Create a LinkedIn post highlighting 3 key benefits of investing in SEO for small businesses, using a bold and energetic tone. Include a call to action to visit Sabkhoj\'s website for a free consultation.', 1, 1, '2026-07-11 11:30:14', '2026-07-11 11:30:14'),
(169, 26, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'PPC Success Reel', 'Develop a reel script for Instagram showcasing a before-and-after scenario of a business struggling with online visibility and then thriving after using Sabkhoj\'s PPC services. Incorporate the \'ppc-success-reel.mp4\' video asset and maintain an energetic, inspiring tone. End with a strong call to action to DM for details.', 2, 1, '2026-07-11 11:30:14', '2026-07-11 11:30:14'),
(170, 26, 'carousel', 'facebook', 'Web Design Carousel', 'Design a 5-slide Facebook carousel post illustrating the importance of professional web design. Each slide should feature a different aspect (e.g., user experience, mobile responsiveness, branding) and include an engaging question. The final slide should promote Sabkhoj\'s web design services with a link to their portfolio.', 3, 1, '2026-07-11 11:30:14', '2026-07-11 11:30:14'),
(171, 26, 'hashtags', 'instagram', 'Digital Marketing Hashtags', 'Generate a list of 10-15 trending and niche-specific hashtags for Sabkhoj\'s Instagram posts, focusing on digital marketing, SEO, PPC, and small business growth in India. Include a mix of broad and specific terms.', 4, 1, '2026-07-11 11:30:14', '2026-07-11 11:30:14'),
(172, 26, 'post', 'x', 'Brand Reputation Tips', 'Write a concise and impactful X (formerly Twitter) post offering 3 quick tips for businesses to improve their online brand reputation. Use emojis and a bold, direct tone. Include a link to Sabkhoj\'s services.', 5, 1, '2026-07-11 11:30:14', '2026-07-11 11:30:14'),
(173, 26, 'thirty_day_plan', 'linkedin', '30-Day Digital Plan', 'Outline a 30-day content plan for Sabkhoj\'s LinkedIn profile, focusing on educating businesses about various digital marketing strategies. Include a mix of posts, articles, and engagement prompts, maintaining a bold and energetic brand voice.', 6, 1, '2026-07-11 11:30:14', '2026-07-11 11:30:14'),
(174, 31, 'post', 'facebook', 'Intro to \'test\' product', 'Create a casual and friendly Facebook post in Hindi introducing our \'test\' product. Focus on a key benefit for \'tees\' and include a call to action to visit our website sabkhoj.in.', 1, 1, '2026-07-13 13:40:03', '2026-07-13 13:40:03'),
(175, 31, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Why \'tees\' love us', 'Develop a short, engaging Instagram Reel script in Hindi featuring a \'tee\' talking about how our \'test\' service has helped them. Keep the tone casual and friendly, and suggest upbeat background music.', 2, 1, '2026-07-13 13:40:03', '2026-07-13 13:40:03'),
(176, 31, 'post', 'x', 'Quick tip for \'tees\'', 'Write a concise and friendly tweet in Hindi offering a quick tip related to our \'test\' product/service that would be useful for \'tees\'. Include relevant hashtags.', 3, 1, '2026-07-13 13:40:03', '2026-07-13 13:40:03'),
(177, 31, 'post', 'facebook', 'Behind the scenes', 'Draft a casual Facebook post in Hindi giving a \'behind the scenes\' look at our team or development process, emphasizing our friendly culture. Ask a question to encourage engagement from \'tees\'.', 4, 1, '2026-07-13 13:40:03', '2026-07-13 13:40:03'),
