(22, 25, 'Professional & authoritative', 'Small and medium business owners, local brick-and-mortar retailers and service providers across India, plus startups and entrepreneurs seeking improved online visibility and lead generation.', 'Business listings and local directory management, SEO and organic search optimization, paid digital advertising and lead generation, website design & development, custom software and e-commerce solutions, plus software training and internet marketing services.', '[\"Business Directory\",\"SEO\",\"Local Business\",\"Digital Marketing\",\"Lead Generation\",\"Web Development\",\"India\"]', '{\"business\":{\"name\":\"sabkhoj  my brand\",\"website\":\"https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in\\/\",\"industry\":\"Other\",\"country\":\"India\",\"language\":\"English\",\"tone\":\"Professional & authoritative\",\"description\":\"\\\"Sabkhoj Informatics Pvt. Ltd. | Web Design | Software Solutions | Digital Marketing Established in 2014, Sabkhoj Informatics Pvt. Ltd. is a trusted name in web development, software solutions, and digital marketing services across India. We specialize in helping businesses grow through tailored business development strategies, e-commerce solutions, custom software, website design & development, and online advertising. Our expert team also offers software training and internet marketing services to ensure your brand stands out in the digital world. Whether you\'re a startup or an established company, we deliver innovative and result-driven solutions that enhance your online presence and customer experience.\\\"\",\"products_services\":\"Business Listings, Digital Marketing, SEO, Lead Generation\",\"target_audience\":\"Business Owners, Local Customers\",\"keywords\":[\"Business Directory\",\"SEO\",\"Local Business\",\"Digital Marketing\",\"India\"]},\"assets\":[{\"id\":151,\"name\":\"Brand logo\",\"type\":\"logo\",\"path\":\"brands\\/logos\\/IvJP0KakuWj9HfPtEH7gjPtx2kzAEfyygqgxwpzp.png\",\"disk\":\"public\",\"metadata\":{\"source\"