ion drive footfall and local searches.\",\"Lead Generation & Conversion: case studies, campaign breakdowns and actionable tips on paid ads, landing pages and sales funnels.\"]},\"suggested_prompts\":[{\"label\":\"30-day Instagram plan\",\"content_type\":\"thirty_day_plan\",\"platform\":\"instagram\",\"prompt_text\":\"Create a 30-day Instagram content calendar for sabkhoj  my brand focused on Indian SMBs and local businesses. Use a professional and authoritative voice. Include 12 educational posts (SEO tips, how business listings work, local SEO checklists), 8 promotional posts (services: web design, lead gen, packages with clear CTAs), 6 testimonial\\/customer success posts with short quotes, and 4 behind-the-scenes\\/culture posts about the team and training. For each day provide: post objective, caption (100-220 characters) with one CTA and one local hashtag, suggested image\\/video idea, and 3-5 hashtags. Emphasize driving website visits to https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in and lead inquiries.\"},{\"label\":\"Reel: Local SEO tip\",\"content_type\":\"reel_script\",\"platform\":\"instagram\",\"prompt_text\":\"Write a 30\\u201345 second Instagram Reel script for sabkhoj  my brand teaching three quick local SEO wins for small shops in India (Google Business Profile optimization, NAP consistency, local keywords). Use a professional & authoritative tone, include on-screen text markers, suggested B-roll or visuals for each point, a short caption (max 150 characters) with CTA to book a free consultation on https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in, and 8 relevant hashtags.\"},{\"label\":\"LinkedIn carousel: case study\",\"content_type\":\"carousel\",\"platform\":\"linkedin\",\"prompt_text\":\"Create a 6-slide LinkedIn carousel for sabkhoj  my brand that presents a concise case study of a local business in India that increased leads using SEO + business listings. Slide breakdown: challenge, strategy, implementation steps, results (metrics), client testimonial, CTA to contact. Provide professional copy for each slide (20\\u201335 words), a descriptive LinkedIn post caption (2\\u20133 short paragraphs) and suggested image\\/graphic guidance for each slide.\"},{\"label\":\"Facebook service post\",\"content_type\":\"post\",\"platform\":\"facebook\",\"prompt_text\":\"Write a professional Facebook post for sabkhoj  my brand promoting the \'Local Business Listing\' service. Include a headline, 2\\u20133 short paragraphs explaining benefits for Indian SMBs, one client mini-testimonial sentence, pricing\\/offer highlight (e.g., free audit), a clear CTA to https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in\\/contact, and 6 local\\/relevant hashtags. Tone: authoritative and trust-building.\"},{\"label\":\"X (Twitter) hashtags set\",\"content_type\":\"hashtags\",\"platform\":\"x\",\"prompt_text\":\"Generate a set of 20 X-friendly hashtags and short hashtag groups (5 each) for sabkhoj  my brand focused on local SEO, digital marketing services in India, web design and lead generation. Prioritize relevance, locality (India\\/cities), and reach. Provide 4 suggested hashtag groupings optimized for: organic SEO tips, lead-generation posts, client testimonials, and event\\/training promotions.\"},{\"label\":\"YouTube explainer video\",\"content_type\":\"reel_script\",\"platform\":\"youtube\",\"prompt_text\":\"Draft a 6\\u20138 minute YouTube video script for sabkhoj  my brand titled \'How to Get More Local Customers: A Practical Guide for Indian Small Businesses\'. Structure: hook, 4 actionable sections (Google Business Profile, local keyword research, on-page SEO, simple paid ad strategies), real examples, brief client success story, and clear CTA to download a free checklist on https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in. Include suggested chapter timestamps, on-screen graphics and closed-caption-ready copy. Tone: professional, instructive, results-focused.\"}],\"provider\":\"bluesminds\",\"model\":\"gpt-5-mini\"}}', 'complete', '2026-07-03 15:33:24', NULL, '2026-07-03 15:29:26', '2026-07-03 15:33:24'),
(23, 26, 'Bold & energetic', 'Small to medium-sized businesses across various industries, including specialized fields like dentistry and veterinary services, seeking to improve their digital presence and customer engagement.', 'Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search (PPC), Social Media Marketing, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They cater to both global web presence and local marketing needs.', '[\"Digital Marketing Agency\",\"SEO Services\",\"Search Engine Optimization\",\"PPC Advertising\",\"Google Ads\",\"Social Media Marketing\",\"Lead Generation\",\"Web Design\"]', '{\"business\":{\"name\":\"sabkhojc\",\"website\":\"https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in\",\"industry\":\"Other\",\"country\":\"India\",\"language\":\"English\",\"tone\":\"Bold & energetic\",\"description\":\"According to TopTenReviews in 2018, as well as many other 3rd party review sites and publications we always comes out on top. We\\u2019re a leading Internet Digital Marketing Company who offers SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, ConsultingLead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design Services.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe strategically help build your brand, improve your global web presence, and develop meaningful relationships with your customers. We also use our local marketing skills to help hundreds of smaller businesses in a variety of industries. Dentists, plumbers, veterinarians, dermatologists, and other specialized industries benefit from our dedicated, professional digital marketing campaigns.\",\"products_services\":\"According to TopTenReviews in 2018, as well as many other 3rd party review sites and publications we always comes out on top. We\\u2019re a leading Internet Digital Marketing Company who offers SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, ConsultingLead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design Services.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe strategically help build your brand, improve your global web presence, and develop meaningful relationships with your customers. We also use our local marketing skills to help hundreds of smaller businesses in a variety of industries. Dentists, plumbers, veterinarians, dermatologists, and other specialized industries benefit from our dedicated, professional digital marketing campaigns.\",\"target_audience\":\"sabkhoj\",\"keywords\":[\"Digital Marketing Digital Marketing Agency SEO Services Search Engine Optimization PPC Advertising Google Ads Social Media Marketing\"]},\"assets\":[{\"id\":167,\"name\":\"logosabkhoj.png\",\"type\":\"image\",\"path\":\"brands\\/26\\/assets\\/ortrjHDJNYcDbLBSydBqu13K3gBYJx8GO0jeiR7r.png\",\"disk\":\"local\",\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"wizard_step_2\"}},{\"id\":168,\"name\":\"Brand logo\",\"type\":\"logo\",\"path\":\"brands\\/logos\\/kcoVgNGvV5fFsqLcJogMrRuqwaXpazoFPILyEuPV.png\",\"disk\":\"public\",\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"brand_create\"}},{\"id\":173,\"name\":\"image-hero-brand-visual.jpg\",\"type\":\"image\",\"path\":\"brands\\/26\\/content_library\\/ai-images\\/image-hero-brand-visual-63b36dde-cf11-4f9f-a257-7ad770690865.jpg\",\"disk\":\"local\",\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"content_library\",\"library_type\":\"image\",\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"generation_prompt\":\"A vibrant, high-angle photorealistic shot of a diverse group of young professionals collaborating energetically around a sleek, modern conference table, bathed in bright, natural light, with a subtle sabkhojc logo subtly integrated into the table surface. The mood is optimistic and innovative.\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"black-forest-labs\\/flux.2-pro\"}},{\"id\":232,\"name\":\"ppc-success-reel.mp4\",\"type\":\"video\",\"path\":\"brands\\/26\\/content_library\\/ai-videos\\/ppc-success-reel-5ae751f7-4066-4161-9e2e-35db195bda07.mp4\",\"disk\":\"local\",\"metadata\":{\"source\":\"content_library\",\"library_type\":\"reel\",\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"generation_prompt\":\"Close-up of a frustrated small business owner staring at a blank computer screen, dim lighting, slow zoom out. Quick cut to a vibrant split-screen showing a bustling online store on one side and a thriving physical store on the other, bright, dynamic lighting, high-energy music. Text overlay: \\\"Boost your reach with Sabkhoj!\\\"\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/veo-3.1-lite\",\"duration_seconds\":8}}],\"urls\":{\"website\":\"https:\\/\\/www.sabkhoj.in\",\"social\":[],\"reference\":[]},\"social_accounts\":[{\"platform\":\"facebook\",\"name\":\"Funny Guru ji Master\",\"handle\":null,\"status\":\"active\"},{\"platform\":\"instagram\",\"name\":\"akvisi9ary\",\"handle\":\"@akvisi9ary\",\"status\":\"active\"}],\"trained_at\":\"2026-07-11T17:00:07+00:00\",\"ai_analysis\":{\"brand_summary\":\"Sabkhoj is a leading Indian digital marketing company specializing in SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design Services. They help businesses, from small local enterprises to larger brands, build their online presence and connect with customers.\",\"detected_tone\":\"Bold & energetic\",\"detected_audience\":\"Small to medium-sized businesses across various industries, including specialized fields like dentistry and veterinary services, seeking to improve their digital presence and customer engagement.\",\"detected_services\":\"Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search (PPC), Social Media Marketing, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They cater to both global web presence and local marketing needs.\",\"top_keywords\":[\"Digital Marketing Agency\",\"SEO Services\",\"Search Engine Optimization\",\"PPC Advertising\",\"Google Ads\",\"Social Media Marketing\",\"Lead Generation\",\"Web Design\"],\"content_strategy\":{\"themes\":[\"educational\",\"promotional\",\"testimonials\",\"culture\"],\"pillars\":[\"Digital Marketing Solutions & Benefits\",\"Client Success Stories & Case Studies\",\"Industry Insights & Trends\",\"Sabkhoj Company Culture & Expertise\"]},\"suggested_prompts\":[{\"label\":\"SEO Benefits Post\",\"content_type\":\"post\",\"platform\":\"linkedin\",\"prompt_text\":\"Create a LinkedIn post highlighting 3 key benefits of investing in SEO for small businesses, using a bold and energetic tone. Include a call to action to visit Sabkhoj\'s website for a free consultation.\"},{\"label\":\"PPC Success Reel\",\"content_type\":\"reel_script\",\"platform\":\"instagram\",\"prompt_text\":\"Develop a reel script for Instagram showcasing a before-and-after scenario of a business struggling with online visibility and then thriving after using Sabkhoj\'s PPC services. Incorporate the \'ppc-success-reel.mp4\' video asset and maintain an energetic, inspiring tone. End with a strong call to action to DM for details.\"},{\"label\":\"Web Design Carousel\",\"content_type\":\"carousel\",\"platform\":\"facebook\",\"prompt_text\":\"Design a 5-slide Facebook carousel post illustrating the importance of professional web design. Each slide should feature a different aspect (e.g., user experience, mobile responsiveness, branding) and include an engaging question. The final slide should promote Sabkhoj\'s web design services with a link to their portfolio.\"},{\"label\":\"Digital Marketing Hashtags\",\"content_type\":\"hashtags\",\"platform\":\"instagram\",\"prompt_text\":\"Generate a list of 10-15 trending and niche-specific hashtags for Sabkhoj\'s Instagram posts, focusing on digital marketing, SEO, PPC, and small business growth in India. Include a mix of broad and specific terms.\"},{\"label\":\"Brand Reputation Tips\",\"content_type\":\"post\",\"platform\":\"x\",\"prompt_text\":\"Write a concise and impactful X (formerly Twitter) post offering 3 quick tips for businesses to improve their online brand reputation. Use emojis and a bold, direct tone. Include a link to Sabkhoj\'s services.\"},{\"label\":\"30-Day Digital Plan\",\"content_type\":\"thirty_day_plan\",\"platform\":\"linkedin\",\"prompt_text\":\"Outline a 30-day content plan for Sabkhoj\'s LinkedIn profile, focusing on educating businesses about various digital marketing strategies. Include a mix of posts, articles, and engagement prompts, maintaining a bold and energetic brand voice.\"}],\"provider\":\"openrouter\",\"model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}}', 'complete', '2026-07-11 11:30:14', NULL, '2026-07-06 13:03:27', '2026-07-11 11:30:14');
