(94, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'instagram', 'Caption: brand awareness', '🔥 STOP SCROLLING, START DISCOVERING! 🔥 Tired of the same old, generic searches and solutions? In a world full of noise, **sabkhojc** is the game-changer you\'ve been waiting for!\n\nWe\'re not just another platform; we\'re your ultimate, curated gateway to the extraordinary. What makes us truly unique? We cut through the clutter, delivering unparalleled insights and truly distinctive options that you simply won\'t find anywhere else. Experience discovery redefined. ✨\n\nReady to unlock a world beyond the ordinary? Click the link in bio and unleash your sabkhojc today!\n\n#sabkhojc #RedefineDiscovery #GameChanger #UniqueSolutions #BeyondTheOrdinary #Innovation #UnleashYourSearch', 'draft', 1, 'Write a Bold & energetic Instagram caption for sabkhojc introducing the brand to sabkhoj. Highlight what makes sabkhojc unique in Other. Include a strong hook and CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: brand awareness\",\"ai_provider\":\"gemini\",\"ai_model\":\"gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-06 14:51:35', '2026-07-06 14:51:35'),
(95, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Image: product showcase', '**Headline:** Proven Excellence. Unmatched Digital Results.\n\n**Visual Direction:**\n*   **Scene:** A vibrant, modern, and open-plan office setting. In the foreground, a diverse team of 3-4 digital marketing professionals (mixed gender, various ethnicities, late 20s-40s) are actively collaborating around a large, interactive digital display or a cluster of high-definition monitors. The atmosphere is energetic and focused, conveying innovation and teamwork.\n*   **Props:** The central display showcases dynamic analytics dashboards: real-time SEO ranking graphs, paid ad performance metrics, social media engagement charts, and a stylized world map with glowing connections representing global reach. On a smaller tablet or laptop held by one team member, a clean website design mock-up is visible, alongside a subtle section dedicated to local client success, featuring small, professional icons for a tooth, a wrench, a paw print, and a magnifying glass. Branded Sabkhojc notebooks and sleek tech accessories are subtly placed on the desk.\n*   **Lighting:** Bright, optimistic, and professional. Abundant natural light streams in from large windows, complemented by modern, warm office lighting, creating a welcoming yet high-tech environment.\n*   **Color Palette:** Clean and contemporary, aligning with Sabkhojc\'s brand identity (e.g., blues, greens, whites, grays) with vibrant, data-driven colors on the digital screens.\n\n**Overlay Text:**\n**Sabkhojc: Your #1 Digital Marketing Partner**\nRanked Top by Industry Leaders (TopTenReviews 2018 & Beyond!)\n**Comprehensive Services:**\nSEO | Paid Search | Social Media | Web Design | Lead Generation | Brand Reputation\n**Global Brand Building & Local Business Growth**\n(Specializing in Dentists, Plumbers, Vets, Dermatologists, and more!)\n\n**Call to Action:** Learn How We Can Grow Your Business Today!\n**Website:** sabkhojc.com', 'draft', 1, 'Design an image post concept for sabkhojc featuring According to TopTenReviews in 2018, as well as many other 3rd party review sites and publications we always comes out on top. We’re a leading Internet Digital Marketing Company who offers SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, ConsultingLead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design Services.\r\n\r\nWe strategically help build your brand, improve your global web presence, and develop meaningful relationships with your customers. We also use our local marketing skills to help hundreds of smaller businesses in a variety of industries. Dentists, plumbers, veterinarians, dermatologists, and other specialized industries benefit from our dedicated, professional digital marketing campaigns.. Describe the scene, props, lighting, and caption overlay for sabkhoj.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"image\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Image: product showcase\",\"ai_provider\":\"gemini\",\"ai_model\":\"gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-06 14:57:31', '2026-07-06 14:57:31'),
(96, 24, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'x', 'Authority X posts', 'Here are 5 Twitter posts for sabkhojnewbrand, positioning it as an authoritative voice in India:\n\n1/5\nDid you know India\'s digital economy is projected to hit $1 trillion by 2025? Don\'t get left behind. Explore key insights for growth: [https://www.sabkhoj.in/](https://www.sabkhoj.in/) #IndiaGrowth #DigitalIndia\n\n2/5\nFact: SME contribution to India\'s GDP is over 30%. Unlock your business\'s full potential with data-driven strategies. Find out how: [https://www.sabkhoj.in/](https://www.sabkhoj.in/) #SMEIndia #BusinessStrategy\n\n3/5\nIndia\'s youth demographic is a powerhouse. Are you effectively engaging this crucial market? Discover actionable insights: [https://www.sabkhoj.in/](https://www.sabkhoj.in/) #YouthPower #IndianMarket\n\n4/5\nRural consumption is a rapidly expanding frontier in India. Tap into untapped opportunities. Learn more here: [https://www.sabkhoj.in/](https://www.sabkhoj.in/) #RuralIndia #ConsumerInsights\n\n5/5\nWhat\'s the biggest challenge your business faces in India\'s dynamic market? Share your thoughts! We\'re here to help you navigate it: [https://www.sabkhoj.in/](https://www.sabkhoj.in/) #IndiaBusiness #MarketChallenges', 'draft', 1, 'Generate 5 X (Twitter) posts for sabkhojnewbrand that position the brand as an authoritative voice in India. Each post should be under 280 characters, include a concise insight or stat-style statement, one actionable takeaway, a short link to https://www.sabkhoj.in/, and 2–3 hashtags. Include one prompt-style question to drive replies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Authority X posts\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 11:46:48', '2026-07-07 11:46:48');
