(97, 24, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'x', 'Image: hero brand visual', '## Sabkhojnewbrand Image Post Creative Brief\n\n**Campaign:** Brand Launch - Hero Identity Showcase\n\n**Objective:** To introduce Sabkhojnewbrand with a professional and authoritative visual, establishing credibility and clarity for Indian businesses and professionals.\n\n**Target Audience:** Indian businesses and professionals seeking reliable, consultative services. Decision-makers and buyers who value credibility, clarity, and measurable outcomes.\n\n---\n\n### **Headline:**\n\n**Unlock Your Business Potential with Sabkhojnewbrand.**\n\n---\n\n### **Visual Direction:**\n\n**Concept:** A clean, modern, and aspirational hero image that subtly integrates brand elements while conveying professionalism and authority.\n\n**Layout:**\n\n*   **Dominant Element:** A sophisticated, abstract geometric pattern or a subtle, stylized gradient that incorporates the brand\'s primary color palette. This should occupy the majority of the background.\n*   **Central Focus:** The Sabkhojnewbrand logo prominently displayed, perhaps subtly animated or given a slight 3D effect to make it stand out without being gaudy.\n*   **Subtle Imagery (Optional, if space allows):** Very faint, blurred outlines of interconnected lines or a subtle network grid in the background to symbolize connection, strategy, and intelligence, without detracting from the brand identity.\n*   **Minimalist Aesthetic:** Avoid clutter. Focus on clean lines, ample negative space, and a refined composition.\n\n**Colors:**\n\n*   **Primary Brand Color:** (Assuming a deep, trustworthy blue or a sophisticated grey-green – *please insert actual brand primary color here, e.g., #003366 (Deep Navy Blue)*) - This should be the dominant hue in the background or gradient.\n*   **Secondary Brand Color:** (Assuming a complementary accent, e.g., #FF9900 (Warm Gold) or #66CCFF (Sky Blue)) - Used sparingly for subtle accents within the geometric pattern or a glow around the logo.\n*   **Neutral Tones:** Off-white, light grey, or very subtle beige for background elements or text contrast to maintain a clean and professional feel.\n*   **Logo Colors:** Ensure the logo\'s official colors are accurately represented.\n\n**Style & Mood:** Professional, authoritative, trustworthy, intelligent, forward-thinking, polished.\n\n---\n\n### **Overlay Text:**\n\n**Primary Overlay Text:**\n\n**Sabkhojnewbrand: Your Partner for Strategic Growth.**\n\n**Secondary Overlay Text (Smaller, below primary):**\n\n**Clarity. Credibility. Measurable Outcomes.**\n\n---\n\n### **Call to Action (CTA):**\n\n**Learn More**\n\n---\n\n**Final Output for Design Team:**\n\n**Headline:** Unlock Your Business Potential with Sabkhojnewbrand.\n\n**Visual:**\n*   **Concept:** Clean, modern, and aspirational hero image with a sophisticated abstract geometric pattern/gradient as the dominant background.\n*   **Central:** Prominent Sabkhojnewbrand logo.\n*   **Subtle Background:** Faint, blurred outlines of interconnected lines or a network grid (optional).\n*   **Colors:**\n    *   Primary: [Insert Sabkhojnewbrand\'s Primary Brand Color Hex Code, e.g., #003366] - Dominant background.\n    *   Secondary: [Insert Sabkhojnewbrand\'s Secondary Brand Color Hex Code, e.g., #FF9900] - Accent.\n    *   Neutrals: Off-white/Light Grey for contrast.\n    *   Logo: Official brand colors.\n*   **Layout:** Ample negative space, clean lines, refined composition.\n\n**Overlay Text:**\n*   **Primary:** Sabkhojnewbrand: Your Partner for Strategic Growth.\n*   **Secondary:** Clarity. Credibility. Measurable Outcomes.\n\n**CTA:** Learn More', 'draft', 1, 'Create an image post brief for sabkhojnewbrand: a clean hero visual showcasing the brand identity. Style: Professional & authoritative. Audience: Listed audience: \"fd\" (placeholder). Likely target: Indian businesses and professionals seeking reliable, consultative services—position content toward decision-makers and buyers who value credibility, clarity, and measurable outcomes.. Include layout, colors, and overlay text suggestions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"image\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Image: hero brand visual\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 11:47:55', '2026-07-07 11:47:55'),
(98, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'x', 'Image: hero brand visual', 'A vibrant, high-angle photorealistic shot of a diverse group of young professionals collaborating energetically around a sleek, modern conference table, bathed in bright, natural light, with a subtle sabkhojc logo subtly integrated into the table surface. The mood is optimistic and innovative.', 'draft', 1, 'Create an image post brief for sabkhojc: a clean hero visual showcasing the brand identity. Style: Bold & energetic. Audience: sabkhoj. Include layout, colors, and overlay text suggestions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"image\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Image: hero brand visual\",\"asset_id\":173,\"image_prompt\":\"A vibrant, high-angle photorealistic shot of a diverse group of young professionals collaborating energetically around a sleek, modern conference table, bathed in bright, natural light, with a subtle sabkhojc logo subtly integrated into the table surface. The mood is optimistic and innovative.\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"black-forest-labs\\/flux.2-pro\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 12:06:15', '2026-07-07 12:06:15'),
