(103, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'instagram', 'Caption: brand awareness', 'Tired of digital marketing that doesn\'t deliver? 🚀\n\n**Sabkhojbrand is here to transform your business\'s online presence.** We\'re not just another agency; we\'re your dedicated digital growth partner, specializing in a unique blend of cutting-edge SaaS solutions and bespoke web development for Indian businesses.\n\nWhat makes Sabkhojbrand different? We go beyond generic strategies. Our proprietary AI-driven analytics platform provides unparalleled insights into your target audience, allowing us to craft hyper-targeted digital marketing campaigns that maximize ROI. Coupled with our agile web development approach, we build not just websites, but high-performing digital assets designed for conversion and scalability. From SEO and SEM to social media and content marketing, we integrate seamlessly to deliver a holistic digital ecosystem that drives real business results.\n\n**Ready to unlock your full digital potential?** Visit our website [Link in Bio] or DM us today for a free consultation and discover how Sabkhojbrand can propel your business forward.\n\n#Sabkhojbrand #DigitalMarketingIndia #WebDevelopmentIndia #SaaS #TechSolutions #BusinessGrowth #IndianBusiness #DigitalTransformation #Innovation #MarketingStrategy #GrowthHacking #B2BMarketing #OnlinePresence #SEOIndia #SEMIndia #IndianStartups', 'draft', 1, 'Write a Professional & authoritative Instagram caption for sabkhojbrand introducing the brand to Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.. Highlight what makes sabkhojbrand unique in SaaS / Tech. Include a strong hook and CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: brand awareness\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 12:27:45', '2026-07-07 12:27:45'),
(104, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: product spotlight', 'Elevate your business in the digital age. 🚀 Sabkhoj offers a complete spectrum of digital marketing and web development services designed for Indian businesses like yours. From boosting your online visibility with expert SEO and Paid Search to crafting engaging Social Media campaigns and building powerful Brand Reputation, we drive tangible results. Need to expand your reach? Our Lead Generation and Business Development strategies are second to none. Plus, with cutting-edge Web Design, Responsive Web Solutions, Android/iOS Development, and reliable Domain & Hosting, we build your digital infrastructure for success.\n\n**Unlock your full potential. Partner with Sabkhoj and transform your digital presence into a powerful growth engine.**\n\nVisit our website today to explore our solutions and schedule a consultation! #Sabkhoj #DigitalMarketingIndia #WebDevelopmentIndia #SEOIndia #PaidSearch #SocialMediaMarketing #LeadGeneration #BrandReputation #BusinessDevelopment #WebDesign #AppDevelopment #IndianBusinesses #DigitalTransformation #GrowYourBusiness', 'draft', 1, 'Create a Professional & authoritative caption for sabkhojbrand promoting Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions.. Target Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions., focus on benefits, and end with a clear call to action.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: product spotlight\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 12:27:47', '2026-07-07 12:27:47'),
(105, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: engagement question', 'Is your business ready to dominate the digital landscape? 🚀\n\nAt Sabkhoj, we empower Indian businesses to achieve unparalleled online success. From strategic SEO and high-impact Paid Search to engaging Social Media and robust Web Design, our comprehensive suite of digital marketing and development solutions is built to drive growth.\n\nWe specialize in:\n* **Digital Marketing:** SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management\n* **Web Development:** Web Design, Business Development, Android/iOS Development, Domain & Hosting, Responsive Web Solutions\n\n**What\'s the #1 digital challenge your business is currently facing? Share your thoughts below! 👇**\n\nLet Sabkhoj be your trusted partner in navigating the complexities of the digital world.\n\n#Sabkhoj #DigitalMarketingIndia #WebDevelopmentIndia #SEOIndia #PaidSearchIndia #SocialMediaMarketing #BusinessGrowth #IndianBusinesses #DigitalTransformation #LeadGeneration #BrandManagement #WebDesignServices', 'draft', 1, 'Write an engaging Professional & authoritative caption for sabkhojbrand that asks Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions. a question related to Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions.. Encourage comments and shares.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: engagement question\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 12:27:50', '2026-07-07 12:27:50'),
