(111, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Lead Gen Reel Script', '## Instagram Reel: Lead Gen Transformation (30 seconds)\n\n**Hook:** (0-3 seconds)\n\n*   **Visual:** Close-up of a frustrated business owner (actor) staring blankly at a laptop screen showing a very low number of website visitors/leads. Head in hands.\n*   **Audio:** Upbeat, slightly frantic background music.\n*   **On-screen Text:** \"Struggling to find new customers?\"\n\n---\n\n**Scene 1: The Problem** (3-10 seconds)\n\n*   **Visual:** Quick montage of the business owner looking stressed: phone not ringing, empty appointment book, looking at a competitor\'s busy storefront.\n*   **Audio:** Music slightly mellows, a sympathetic tone.\n*   **On-screen Text:** \"Low leads = Stagnant growth 📉\"\n\n---\n\n**Scene 2: The Turning Point** (10-15 seconds)\n\n*   **Visual:** Business owner looking determined, then a quick shot of them typing \"Sabkhoj\" into a search bar. A bright, clean Sabkhoj logo appears briefly.\n*   **Audio:** Music picks up, more optimistic.\n*   **On-screen Text:** \"Time for a change. Time for Sabkhoj!\"\n\n---\n\n**Scene 3: The Solution (Sabkhoj in action)** (15-23 seconds)\n\n*   **Visual:** Fast-paced, engaging shots:\n    *   A Sabkhoj dashboard with graphs showing upward trends in leads.\n    *   A phone ringing, business owner smiling as they answer.\n    *   A \"New Lead!\" notification popping up.\n    *   A full appointment book.\n    *   A happy customer shaking the business owner\'s hand.\n*   **Audio:** Energetic, positive music. Sound effects: phone ringing, notification chime.\n*   **On-screen Text:**\n    *   \"Targeted Lead Generation\"\n    *   \"Qualified Prospects\"\n    *   \"Real Business Growth!\"\n\n---\n\n**Scene 4: The Transformation & CTA** (23-30 seconds)\n\n*   **Visual:** Business owner smiling confidently, giving a thumbs up. A vibrant, successful business environment in the background (e.g., busy cafe, full workshop).\n*   **Audio:** Music crescendos to an inspiring, triumphant note.\n*   **On-screen Text:**\n    *   \"Transform Your Business Today!\"\n    *   \"Sabkhoj: Your Growth Partner\"\n    *   **CTA:** \"Visit Sabkhoj.com (Link in Bio)\"\n*   **Final Visual:** Sabkhoj logo prominently displayed.', 'draft', 1, 'Develop a 30-second Instagram Reel script demonstrating how effective lead generation can transform a business. Use a \'problem-solution\' format, with Sabkhoj as the solution. Include on-screen text ideas and a clear call to action.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Lead Gen Reel Script\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:19:37', '2026-07-07 12:29:04', '2026-07-07 14:19:37'),
(112, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Reel: 3-second hook', '**Reel Script: Sabkhoj - Your Digital Powerhouse**\n\n**Video Length:** 30 seconds\n**Tone:** Professional & Authoritative\n**Audience:** Businesses in India\n\n---\n\n**(0-3 seconds) HOOK - Scene 1: Dynamic, Fast-Paced Graphics**\n\n*   **Visual:** Rapidly flashing words like \"STRUGGLING?\", \"INVISIBLE ONLINE?\", \"LOSING CUSTOMERS?\" overlaid with a red \"X\" across each. Then a bold, impactful \"NOT ANYMORE.\" emerges.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** NOT ANYMORE.\n*   **Audio:** Sharp, impactful sound effect (e.g., whoosh, short electronic beat).\n*   **Voiceover (V.O.):** (Deep, confident, urgent) **Is your business invisible online?**\n\n**(3-8 seconds) Scene 2: Split Screen - Before & After**\n\n*   **Visual:** Left side: A blurry, generic website on a laptop. Right side: A sleek, modern, mobile-responsive website design. Transition from left to right.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** BEFORE ➡️ AFTER\n*   **Audio:** Upbeat, professional background music begins.\n*   **V.O.:** Sabkhoj transforms your digital presence.\n\n**(8-12 seconds) Scene 3: Icon Montage - Digital Marketing Services**\n\n*   **Visual:** Quick succession of animated icons representing SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, and Lead Generation. Each icon appears briefly and then transitions to the next.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** SEO. Paid Search. Social. Leads.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues.\n*   **V.O.:** From comprehensive SEO to powerful lead generation...\n\n**(12-16 seconds) Scene 4: Icon Montage - Web & App Development**\n\n*   **Visual:** Quick succession of animated icons representing Web Design, Android/iOS Development, and Responsive Web.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** Web Design. App Dev. Responsive.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues.\n*   **V.O.:** ...and cutting-edge web & app development...\n\n**(16-20 seconds) Scene 5: Professional Consultation**\n\n*   **Visual:** Two well-dressed professionals (one Sabkhoj, one client) shaking hands in a modern office setting, looking engaged. Overlaid with subtle graphics indicating \"Consulting\" and \"Strategy.\"\n*   **On-Screen Text:** Expert Consulting. Brand Reputation.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues.\n*   **V.O.:** We build your brand, manage your reputation, and drive growth.\n\n**(20-24 seconds) Scene 6: Sabkhoj Logo Reveal with Key Services**\n\n*   **Visual:** Sabkhoj logo animates onto the screen. Key services (Domain & Hosting, Business Dev) appear briefly around it.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** Sabkhoj. Your COMPLETE Digital Partner.\n*   **Audio:** Music swells slightly.\n*   **V.O.:** Domain, hosting, business development – we do it all.\n\n**(24-27 seconds) Scene 7: Call to Action - Dynamic Text & Website URL**\n\n*   **Visual:** Bold, animated text for the CTA. Sabkhoj website URL clearly displayed.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** LEVEL UP YOUR BUSINESS. Visit Sabkhoj.com\n*   **Audio:** Music becomes more prominent.\n*   **V.O.:** **Ready to dominate your market?**\n\n**(27-30 seconds) Scene 8: Final Sabkhoj Branding & Contact Info**\n\n*   **Visual:** Sabkhoj logo prominently displayed. Contact details (phone icon, email icon) appear briefly.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** Sabkhoj.com | #DigitalSuccess #IndiaBusiness\n*   **Audio:** Music fades out with a final, confident note.\n*   **V.O.:** **Contact Sabkhoj today!**\n\n---', 'draft', 1, 'Write a 30-second reel script for sabkhojbrand with a bold hook in the first 3 seconds. Topic: Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions.. Tone: Professional & authoritative. Audience: Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.. Include scene directions and CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Reel: 3-second hook\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:19:29', '2026-07-07 12:29:11', '2026-07-07 14:19:29'),
(113, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Reel: quick tip', '## Sabkhoj Brand - Digital Solutions Tip (15-30s Reel)\n\n**Hook (0-3s)**\n\n*   **Visual:** Fast-paced montage of a modern, sleek website, a data dashboard, and a mobile app screen.\n*   **Audio:** Upbeat, professional, slightly energetic background music starts.\n*   **On-Screen Text:** \"Indian Businesses: Digital Edge?\"\n\n**Scene 1 (3-8s)**\n\n*   **Visual:** Close-up of a professional, diverse team collaborating around a laptop, gesturing towards a screen with a sophisticated UI.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues.\n*   **Voiceover (Professional, authoritative male voice):** \"In India\'s dynamic market, your digital presence isn\'t an option, it\'s a strategic imperative.\"\n*   **On-Screen Text:** \"Strategic Digital Presence\"\n\n**Scene 2 (8-15s)**\n\n*   **Visual:** Split screen: Left side shows a generic, outdated website. Right side shows a modern, responsive, user-friendly sabkhojbrand-style website. Arrow pointing from left to right.\n*   **Audio:** Music slightly swells.\n*   **Voiceover:** \"For SaaS and Tech, focus on scalable architecture and seamless user experience.\"\n*   **On-Screen Text:** \"Scalable Architecture. Seamless UX.\"\n\n**Scene 3 (15-22s)**\n\n*   **Visual:** Quick cuts of a mobile app, a cloud icon, and a secure data lock icon.\n*   **Audio:** Music becomes slightly more impactful.\n*   **Voiceover:** \"This ensures agility, security, and a competitive edge in a rapidly evolving landscape.\"\n*   **On-Screen Text:** \"Agility. Security. Competitive Edge.\"\n\n**CTA (22-30s)**\n\n*   **Visual:** Sabkhoj Brand logo prominently displayed. Contact information (website/email) appears below.\n*   **Audio:** Music fades slightly, then ends with a final, crisp note.\n*   **Voiceover:** \"Ready to transform your digital journey? Connect with Sabkhoj Brand today.\"\n*   **On-Screen Text:**\n    \"Sabkhoj Brand\"\n    \"Your Digital Growth Partner\"\n    \"Visit sabkhojbrand.com\"\n    \"DM us to learn more!\"', 'draft', 1, 'Create a 15–30s reel script for sabkhojbrand sharing one quick tip for Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions. about SaaS / Tech. Keep it Professional & authoritative and end with a follow CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Reel: quick tip\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:19:15', '2026-07-07 12:29:15', '2026-07-07 14:19:15'),
(114, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Reel: product demo', '**Reel Title', 'draft', 1, 'Script a product demo reel for sabkhojbrand showing Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions. in action. Target Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.. Include hook, demo beats, and closing CTA in a Professional & authoritative voice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Reel: product demo\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:19:21', '2026-07-07 12:29:19', '2026-07-07 14:19:21'),
(115, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'x', 'Reel: trend adaptation', '## SabKhoj Brand - \"Unlock Your Business Potential\" Reel Script\n\n**Format:** Fast-paced, trending \"Before & After\" style with quick cuts and impactful text.\n\n**Target Audience:** Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.\n\n**Tone:** Professional & Authoritative\n\n---\n\n**(0-2 seconds) HOOK - High-energy, impactful visual**\n\n*   **Visual:** Rapid fire montage of common business pain points (e.g., empty website analytics, a \"Coming Soon\" page, a sad-looking \"Open\" sign, a phone not ringing). Each shot is *very* brief, almost subliminal.\n*   **Audio:** Upbeat, professional, slightly dramatic intro music sting.\n*   **On-screen Text (Quick Flash):** \"STRUGGLING TO GROW?\"\n\n---\n\n**(2-4 seconds) SCENE 1 - The \"Before\" Problem**\n\n*   **Visual:** Split screen. Left side: A generic, outdated, or slow-loading website on a desktop. Right side: A small business owner looking frustrated at their phone, trying to gain traction.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues, slightly more prominent. Sound of a slow-loading page or a sigh.\n*   **On-screen Text (Left Side):** \"GENERIC WEBSITE?\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Right Side):** \"ZERO ONLINE LEADS?\"\n\n---\n\n**(4-6 seconds) SCENE 2 - The \"Before\" Problem (Continued)**\n\n*   **Visual:** Split screen. Left side: A social media feed with very few likes/comments on a business post. Right side: A map with very few pins, suggesting limited local visibility.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues. Subtle \"crickets\" sound effect.\n*   **On-screen Text (Left Side):** \"INVISIBLE ONLINE?\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Right Side):** \"MISSED OPPORTUNITIES?\"\n\n---\n\n**(6-8 seconds) TRANSITION - The Solution Arrives**\n\n*   **Visual:** A dynamic, almost futuristic \"wipe\" or \"zoom\" transition, revealing the SabKhoj Brand logo prominently.\n*   **Audio:** Music builds slightly, a subtle \"whoosh\" sound effect.\n*   **On-screen Text (Bold, Center):** \"SABKHOJ BRAND PRESENTS...\"\n\n---\n\n**(8-10 seconds) SCENE 3 - The \"After\" Solution: Web Development**\n\n*   **Visual:** Split screen. Left side: A sleek, modern, mobile-responsive website design (mock-up). Right side: A business owner smiling confidently, looking at a tablet with the new website.\n*   **Audio:** Music becomes more uplifting and empowering.\n*   **On-screen Text (Left Side):** \"CUSTOM WEB DEVELOPMENT\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Right Side):** \"ENGAGING USER EXPERIENCE\"\n\n---\n\n**(10-12 seconds) SCENE 4 - The \"After\" Solution: Digital Marketing**\n\n*   **Visual:** Split screen. Left side: A vibrant social media dashboard showing increasing engagement (likes, comments, shares). Right side: A map with many pins, indicating strong local and wider reach.\n*   **Audio:** Music continues to be positive. Subtle \"notification\" sounds.\n*   **On-screen Text (Left Side):** \"STRATEGIC DIGITAL MARKETING\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Right Side):** \"MAXIMUM ONLINE VISIBILITY\"\n\n---\n\n**(12-14 seconds) SCENE 5 - The \"After\" Results**\n\n*   **Visual:** A quick montage of positive business outcomes: website analytics showing growth, a busy \"Open\" sign, a phone ringing off the hook, a successful e-commerce transaction.\n*   **Audio:** Music peaks. Sound of a cash register, a happy customer, a phone ringing.\n*   **On-screen Text (Quick Flash):** \"INCREASED LEADS!\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Quick Flash):** \"BOOSTED SALES!\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Quick Flash):** \"GROWING YOUR BUSINESS!\"\n\n---\n\n**(14-15 seconds) CTA - Direct Call to Action**\n\n*   **Visual:** SabKhoj Brand logo prominently displayed. A clear, professional graphic with contact information.\n*   **Audio:** Music fades slightly, then ends cleanly.\n*   **On-screen Text (Large, Clear):** \"READY TO UNLOCK YOUR POTENTIAL?\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Smaller, Below):** \"Visit sabkhojbrand.com\"\n*   **On-screen Text (Even Smaller, Below):** \"DM us for a FREE Consultation\"\n\n---\n\n**(End Screen / Final Frame)**\n\n*   **Visual:** SabKhoj Brand logo and website address.\n*   **On-screen Text:** sabkhojbrand.com | Digital Marketing | Web Development | Grow Your Business in India\n\n---', 'draft', 1, 'Adapt a trending reel format for sabkhojbrand to reach Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.. Theme: promotional. Tone: Professional & authoritative. Provide shot list and on-screen text.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Reel: trend adaptation\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:19:07', '2026-07-07 12:29:26', '2026-07-07 14:19:07'),
(116, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Web Design Carousel', 'Here\'s a complete Instagram carousel post for Sabkhojbrand, showcasing the \"5 Elements of a High-Converting Responsive Website.\"\n\n---\n\n**Carousel Post Content**\n\n**Slide 1: Cover Slide**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** A vibrant, split-screen image. One side shows a sleek, modern website on a desktop, the other side shows the same website perfectly adapted to a smartphone screen. A subtle arrow or \"resize\" icon could bridge the two.\n*   **Heading:** 🚀 Unlock Your Online Potential: 5 Elements of a High-Converting Responsive Website\n*   **Copy:** Is your website truly working for you? In today\'s digital world, a beautiful site isn\'t enough. It needs to convert visitors into customers, no matter how they find you. Swipe to discover the secrets! #SabkhojBrand #WebDesign #ResponsiveDesign #WebsiteConversion #DigitalMarketingTips\n\n---\n\n**Slide 2: Element 1**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** A magnifying glass hovering over a clean, well-organized website navigation menu on a desktop, with the same menu perfectly stacked and accessible via a \"hamburger\" icon on a mobile device.\n*   **Heading:** 1️⃣ Intuitive Navigation & User Experience (UX)\n*   **Copy:** **Why it matters:** Visitors should effortlessly find what they need. Confusing menus or cluttered layouts lead to frustration and high bounce rates.\n    **Responsive Impact:** A seamless experience across all devices – from clear desktop menus to accessible mobile navigation. Easy to use = easy to convert! #UXDesign #WebsiteNavigation #UserFriendly #SabkhojTips\n\n---\n\n**Slide 3: Element 2**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** A split image: one side shows a slow-loading website with a spinning wheel icon; the other side shows a lightning bolt icon or a stopwatch indicating fast loading, with the same website appearing instantly.\n*   **Heading:** 2️⃣ Blazing Fast Loading Speed\n*   **Copy:** **Why it matters:** Every second counts! Studies show 40% of users abandon a website if it takes longer than 3 seconds to load.\n    **Responsive Impact:** Optimized images, minimized code, and efficient server responses ensure your site loads quickly on any connection, preventing lost leads. #WebsiteSpeed #PageLoadTime #SEO #FastWebsite #SabkhojExpertise\n\n---\n\n**Slide 4: Element 3**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** A compelling hero section of a website with a clear headline, a vibrant image, and a prominent call-to-action button (e.g., \"Shop Now,\" \"Get a Quote\"). Show it adapting beautifully from desktop to mobile.\n*   **Heading:** 3️⃣ Clear & Compelling Calls-to-Action (CTAs)\n*   **Copy:** **Why it matters:** What do you want your visitors to do next? Your CTAs should be obvious, enticing, and strategically placed to guide them towards conversion.\n    **Responsive Impact:** CTAs that are clickable on any screen size, stand out visually, and use persuasive language to drive desired actions. Make it easy to say \"YES!\" #CTA #CallToAction #ConversionRate #MarketingStrategy #SabkhojSolutions\n\n---\n\n**Slide 5: Element 4**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** A split-screen showing a form field on a desktop (e.g., \"Name,\" \"Email,\" \"Message\") and the same form fields perfectly sized for mobile input, with large, finger-friendly buttons.\n*   **Heading:** 4️⃣ Mobile-First Design & Form Optimization\n*   **Copy:** **Why it matters:** Over half of all web traffic comes from mobile devices. If your site isn\'t designed for mobile first, you\'re missing out.\n    **Responsive Impact:** Forms that are easy to fill out on a small screen, content that\'s readable without pinching and zooming, and elements that are easily tappable. A smooth mobile experience is non-negotiable. #MobileFirst #MobileDesign #FormOptimization #ResponsiveWeb #SabkhojWeb\n\n---\n\n**Slide 6: Element 5**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** A split image. One side shows an analytics dashboard with rising conversion rates or positive user feedback. The other side shows a team discussing website changes based on data.\n*   **Heading:** 5️⃣ Analytics & Continuous Optimization\n*   **Copy:** **Why it matters:** You can\'t improve what you don\'t measure. Data tells you what\'s working, what\'s not, and where to focus your efforts.\n    **Responsive Impact:** Tracking user behavior across devices helps you understand specific pain points and opportunities for improvement, ensuring your site evolves for maximum conversions. #WebAnalytics #DataDriven #Optimization #ContinuousImprovement #SabkhojInsights\n\n---\n\n**Slide 7: Call to Action**\n\n*   **Image Idea:** The Sabkhojbrand logo prominently displayed. Behind it, a sleek, modern website outline (could be a wireframe or a subtle, blurred image of a high-converting site).\n*   **Heading:** Ready for a Website That Converts?\n*   **Copy:** Don\'t let a static website hold your business back. At Sabkhoj, we craft high-converting, responsive websites designed to engage your audience and drive real results.\n    **Let\'s build your online success story!**\n    👉 **Visit our website (Link in Bio)**\n    💬 **DM us to start a conversation**\n    #SabkhojBrand #WebDesignServices #GetAWebsite #DigitalTransformation #BusinessGrowth #WebsiteRedesign #ContactUs\n\n---', 'draft', 1, 'Design an Instagram carousel post showcasing \'5 Elements of a High-Converting Responsive Website\'. Each slide should feature a different element with a brief explanation and a visual idea. End with a call to action for Sabkhoj\'s web design services.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Web Design Carousel\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:18:43', '2026-07-07 12:29:36', '2026-07-07 14:18:43'),
(117, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Carousel: educational slides', 'Here\'s a 5-slide Instagram carousel post for Sabkhoj Brand, ready to publish:\n\n---\n\n**Slide 1: Cover Slide**\n\n**Heading: Unlock Your Business\'s Digital Potential with Sabkhoj Brand**\n\n**Copy:** In today\'s competitive landscape, a robust digital presence is non-negotiable. Sabkhoj Brand empowers Indian businesses to thrive online with comprehensive, tailored solutions.\n\n**Visual Direction:** A dynamic, modern graphic depicting interconnected digital elements (SEO icon, social media icons, website wireframe) forming a cohesive network. Subtle brand colors.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 2: Your All-in-One Digital Marketing Partner**\n\n**Heading: Comprehensive Digital Marketing Solutions**\n\n**Copy:** From boosting visibility to driving conversions, our expert team covers every aspect of your digital journey. We specialize in SEO, Paid Search, Social Media Marketing, and crucial Consulting services.\n\n**Visual Direction:** A clean infographic-style graphic showcasing icons for SEO, PPC, Social Media, and Consulting, linked together with arrows indicating a seamless flow.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 3: Driving Growth & Building Trust**\n\n**Heading: Generate Leads & Cultivate Your Brand**\n\n**Copy:** Sabkhoj Brand goes beyond clicks, focusing on tangible results. We excel in targeted Lead Generation strategies and proactive Brand Reputation Management to build lasting customer trust.\n\n**Visual Direction:** Two distinct sections: one with a magnifying glass over a lead magnet icon, and the other with a shield protecting a brand logo, symbolizing reputation management.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 4: Your Digital Foundation, Built for Success**\n\n**Heading: Expert Web Development & Infrastructure**\n\n**Copy:** A powerful online presence starts with a solid foundation. We offer cutting-edge Web Design, Responsive Web Solutions, and seamless Domain & Hosting services for optimal performance.\n\n**Visual Direction:** A split screen: one side showing a sleek, modern website mock-up on various devices (desktop, tablet, phone), the other side with icons representing domain and hosting.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 5: Beyond the Web: Innovation & Expansion**\n\n**Heading: Accelerate Your Business with Sabkhoj**\n\n**Copy:** Our expertise extends to innovative solutions like Android/iOS App Development and strategic Business Development. Partner with Sabkhoj Brand to expand your reach and secure your future.\n\n**Visual Direction:** A graphic showcasing a smartphone and tablet displaying a generic app interface, with a handshake icon or a growth chart in the background, symbolizing business development.', 'draft', 1, 'Design a 5-slide Instagram carousel for sabkhojbrand educating Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions. about Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions.. Each slide: heading + 2–3 lines + visual direction. Tone: Professional & authoritative.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Carousel: educational slides\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:18:50', '2026-07-07 12:29:41', '2026-07-07 14:18:50');
