(118, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Carousel: step-by-step guide', 'Here\'s a carousel post designed for Sabkhoj Brand, targeting businesses in India seeking comprehensive digital solutions:\n\n---\n\n**Carousel Post for Sabkhoj Brand**\n\n**Slide 1/7 - Image: A sleek, modern graphic with the Sabkhoj logo and the headline \"Unlock Your Business\'s Digital Potential.\"**\n\n**Headline: Unlock Your Business\'s Digital Potential.**\n\n**Copy:** In today\'s competitive landscape, a powerful digital presence isn\'t just an advantage – it\'s a necessity. Sabkhoj Brand empowers Indian businesses to thrive online, offering a comprehensive suite of digital marketing and web development solutions tailored to your unique needs.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 2/7 - Image: A graphic showcasing a magnifying glass over a search bar, with keywords like \"SEO,\" \"Paid Search,\" \"Lead Gen.\"**\n\n**Headline: Dominate Search & Attract Your Audience.**\n\n**Copy:** Is your business easily found by potential customers? Sabkhoj\'s expert **SEO** strategies ensure top rankings, while our targeted **Paid Search** campaigns deliver immediate visibility. We specialize in **Lead Generation**, driving qualified prospects directly to your sales funnel.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 3/7 - Image: A graphic of social media icons (Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn) with a growth arrow.**\n\n**Headline: Build & Nurture Your Brand Online.**\n\n**Copy:** Cultivate a strong online identity with Sabkhoj. Our **Social Media Marketing** expertise connects you with your audience, fostering engagement and loyalty. We actively manage your **Brand Reputation**, ensuring a positive and consistent image across all digital touchpoints.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 4/7 - Image: A graphic of a modern, responsive website template on various devices (desktop, tablet, mobile).**\n\n**Headline: Crafting Digital Experiences That Convert.**\n\n**Copy:** Your website is your digital storefront. Sabkhoj offers cutting-edge **Web Design** and **Responsive Web** solutions, ensuring a seamless and engaging user experience on any device. We also provide secure **Domain and Hosting** services for complete peace of mind.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 5/7 - Image: A graphic of a mobile phone screen displaying a custom app interface.**\n\n**Headline: Innovate with Bespoke Mobile Solutions.**\n\n**Copy:** Reach your customers wherever they are. Sabkhoj specializes in **Android/iOS Development**, creating intuitive and powerful mobile applications that extend your brand\'s reach and enhance customer interaction. Transform your ideas into functional, user-friendly apps.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 6/7 - Image: A graphic of a handshake or interconnected gears, representing partnership and growth.**\n\n**Headline: Strategic Growth & Expert Guidance.**\n\n**Copy:** Beyond individual services, Sabkhoj acts as your strategic partner. Our **Digital Marketing Consulting** provides invaluable insights, while our **Business Development** services help identify new opportunities for expansion and sustained growth.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 7/7 - Image: Sabkhoj Brand logo prominently displayed with a clear, inviting call to action.**\n\n**Headline: Ready to Transform Your Digital Journey?**\n\n**Copy:** Stop guessing, start growing. Sabkhoj Brand is your one-stop solution for all your digital marketing and web development needs. Let us help you achieve measurable results and elevate your business to new heights.\n\n**Call to Action:** Visit SabkhojBrand.com today for a free consultation!\n**Social Handle:** @SabkhojBrand\n\n---', 'draft', 1, 'Create a step-by-step carousel for sabkhojbrand walking Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions. through how to use Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions.. 5–7 slides with Professional & authoritative copy and CTA on the last slide.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Carousel: step-by-step guide\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:18:59', '2026-07-07 12:29:47', '2026-07-07 14:18:59'),
(119, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Carousel: myths vs facts', 'Here\'s a carousel post for SabKojBrand, targeting Indian businesses seeking digital marketing and web development solutions:\n\n---\n\n**Carousel Post: SabKojBrand**\n\n---\n\n**Slide 1: Cover Slide**\n\n**Headline: Digital Marketing & Web Dev: Unmasking the Truths for Indian Businesses**\n\n**Image:** A split image – one side with a question mark over a cloudy, abstract background, the other with a magnifying glass over a clear, brightly lit digital interface. SabKojBrand logo prominent.\n\n**Copy:** In the fast-evolving digital landscape, separating fact from fiction is crucial for your business\'s success. At SabKojBrand, we empower Indian businesses with cutting-edge digital marketing and web development solutions. Let\'s debunk some common myths and reveal the impactful truths.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 2: Myth 1 vs. Fact 1**\n\n**Headline: Myth: \"A Website is Just an Online Brochure.\"**\n\n**Image:** A faded, static image of a generic brochure on one side, contrasting with a dynamic, interactive screenshot of a modern, responsive website on the other.\n\n**Copy:**\n**MYTH:** Many believe a website\'s sole purpose is to display information, much like a static brochure.\n**FACT:** Your website is your 24/7 digital storefront, a lead generation engine, a customer service portal, and a powerful brand-building tool. With strategic design and development, it drives conversions and engagement.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 3: Myth 2 vs. Fact 2**\n\n**Headline: Myth: \"SEO is a One-Time Fix.\"**\n\n**Image:** A broken wrench next to a \"fix it\" sign on one side, contrasted with a growth chart with an upward arrow and a magnifying glass icon on the other.\n\n**Copy:**\n**MYTH:** Businesses often think a quick SEO audit will ensure top rankings forever.\n**FACT:** SEO is an ongoing, dynamic process. Search engine algorithms constantly evolve, and your competitors are always optimizing. Continuous monitoring, content updates, and technical adjustments are essential for sustained visibility and organic growth.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 4: Myth 3 vs. Fact 3**\n\n**Headline: Myth: \"Social Media is Only for B2C Businesses.\"**\n\n**Image:** A \'dislike\' button icon over a generic B2C product on one side, contrasted with a professional networking icon (like LinkedIn) with a handshake on the other.\n\n**Copy:**\n**MYTH:** The misconception is that social media marketing is only effective for reaching individual consumers.\n**FACT:** For B2B businesses, platforms like LinkedIn, Twitter, and even industry-specific Facebook groups are powerful tools for thought leadership, lead generation, talent acquisition, and building industry authority. Strategic content drives professional engagement.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 5: Myth 4 vs. Fact 4**\n\n**Headline: Myth: \"Any Digital Ad Campaign Will Work.\"**\n\n**Image:** A generic \"AD\" banner with no specific targeting, looking lost, on one side, contrasted with a bullseye target with data points and a dollar sign on the other.\n\n**Copy:**\n**MYTH:** Simply running ads on any platform is believed to guarantee results.\n**FACT:** Effective digital advertising requires meticulous audience targeting, compelling ad copy, A/B testing, and continuous performance analysis. Without a data-driven strategy, ad spend can be wasted. We focus on ROI-driven campaigns.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 6: Myth 5 vs. Fact 5**\n\n**Headline: Myth: \"Cheap is Always Best for Web Development.\"**\n\n**Image:** A collapsing, poorly constructed building on one side, contrasted with a robust, modern architectural design on the other.\n\n**Copy:**\n**MYTH:** Opting for the lowest-cost web development solution is seen as a smart budget move.\n**FACT:** Cheap development often leads to poor user experience, security vulnerabilities, limited scalability, and higher maintenance costs in the long run. Investing in quality ensures a robust, future-proof, and high-performing digital asset.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 7: Call to Action**\n\n**Headline: Ready to Build Your Digital Future on Facts?**\n\n**Image:** A clean, professional image of a team collaborating around a digital interface, or a hand pointing towards the SabKojBrand logo.\n\n**Copy:** Don\'t let myths hold your business back. At SabKojBrand, we combine expertise with innovation to deliver verifiable results in digital marketing and web development. Partner with us to build a strong, sustainable digital presence.\n\n**Call to Action:**\nVisit SabKojBrand.com or DM us to schedule a free consultation!\n#SabKojBrand #DigitalMarketing #WebDevelopment #SaaS #Tech #IndianBusiness #MythsVsFacts #DigitalStrategy #SEO #SocialMediaMarketing #WebsiteDesign #BusinessGrowth', 'draft', 1, 'Write a myths-vs-facts carousel for sabkhojbrand in SaaS / Tech. Target Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.. Professional & authoritative tone. One myth/fact pair per slide with punchy headlines.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Carousel: myths vs facts\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:18:34', '2026-07-07 12:29:55', '2026-07-07 14:18:34'),
(120, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Carousel: feature breakdown', 'Here\'s a carousel post for Sabkhojbrand, ready to publish:\n\n---\n\n**Carousel Post for Sabkhojbrand**\n\n**Slide 1: Image: A vibrant, interconnected network of digital icons (magnifying glass, social media logos, gears, lightbulb, computer screen) with \"Sabkhoj\" logo subtly integrated.**\n\n**Heading: Unlock Your Digital Potential with Sabkhoj!**\n\n**Copy:** In today\'s competitive landscape, a strong digital presence isn\'t an option – it\'s a necessity. But navigating the digital world can be complex. Sabkhoj simplifies it for you, offering a comprehensive suite of services designed to propel your business forward. Ready to transform your online strategy? Let\'s explore how!\n\n---\n\n**Slide 2: Image: A graphic showing a magnifying glass over a search bar, with arrows pointing to increased traffic and rankings.**\n\n**Heading: Dominate Search & Drive Traffic**\n\n**Copy:** Get found where it matters most! Our expert SEO strategies ensure your business ranks high on search engines, bringing organic, high-intent traffic to your doorstep. Complement this with targeted Paid Search campaigns that deliver immediate results and maximize your ROI. Stop guessing, start growing!\n\n---\n\n**Slide 3: Image: A collage of popular social media icons, with a speech bubble representing engagement and a graph showing growth.**\n\n**Heading: Build Your Brand & Connect with Customers**\n\n**Copy:** From engaging content to strategic campaigns, our Social Media Marketing services help you build a thriving online community and amplify your brand\'s voice. Need more than just likes? Our Lead Generation expertise turns interest into valuable customer connections, while Brand Reputation Management safeguards your image online.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 4: Image: A split screen showing a professional consulting session on one side and a sleek, modern website design on the other.**\n\n**Heading: Expert Guidance & Stunning Web Solutions**\n\n**Copy:** Gain a competitive edge with our Digital Marketing Consulting, providing tailored strategies for your unique business needs. And when it comes to your online storefront, our Web Design team crafts visually stunning, user-friendly, and Responsive Web solutions that look perfect on any device. Your website, reimagined.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 5: Image: Icons representing mobile apps (Android/iOS), a globe for domain/hosting, and a handshake for business development.**\n\n**Heading: Expand Your Reach & Future-Proof Your Business**\n\n**Copy:** Innovate and scale with Sabkhoj! Our Business Development services help you identify new opportunities and forge strategic partnerships. Looking to go mobile? We offer robust Android/iOS Development. Plus, secure your online foundation with our reliable Domain and Hosting solutions. Everything you need, under one roof.\n\n---\n\n**Slide 6: Image: A clear, clean image of the Sabkhoj logo with a \"Contact Us\" button overlay.**\n\n**Heading: Ready to Elevate Your Digital Journey?**\n\n**Copy:** Stop wishing for digital success and start achieving it with Sabkhoj! Whether you\'re looking to boost sales, build your brand, or create a powerful online presence, we have the expertise and solutions for you.\n\n**Call to Action:** Visit our website or DM us today for a free consultation!\n**[Link to your website here]**\n\n---', 'draft', 1, 'Plan a feature breakdown carousel for sabkhojbrand highlighting key benefits of Sabkhoj offers a comprehensive suite of digital marketing services including SEO, Paid Search, Social Media, Consulting, Lead Generation, Brand Reputation Management, and Web Design. They also provide Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, and Responsive Web solutions.. Audience: Businesses in India seeking digital marketing and web development solutions.. Slide 1 hook, slides 2–5 features, final slide CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Carousel: feature breakdown\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', '2026-07-07 14:18:23', '2026-07-07 12:30:01', '2026-07-07 14:18:23'),
(121, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Web Design Carousel', 'A vibrant, clean website homepage displayed on a desktop monitor, a tablet, and a smartphone, all seamlessly connected by a subtle, glowing line. The design is modern and user-friendly. Text overlay: \'1. Responsive Design: Flawless on Every Device\'', 'draft', 1, 'Design an Instagram carousel post showcasing \'5 Elements of a High-Converting Responsive Website\'. Each slide should feature a different element with a brief explanation and a visual idea. End with a call to action for Sabkhoj\'s web design services.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Web Design Carousel\",\"carousel_group\":\"e3c49d64-ded4-4010-b2a1-4b5225ca48c1\",\"carousel_asset_ids\":[185,186,187,188],\"asset_id\":185,\"carousel_slide_prompts\":[\"A vibrant, clean website homepage displayed on a desktop monitor, a tablet, and a smartphone, all seamlessly connected by a subtle, glowing line. The design is modern and user-friendly. Text overlay: \'1. Responsive Design: Flawless on Every Device\'\",\"A close-up of a website\'s \'Add to Cart\' button, glowing subtly, with a clear, concise headline next to it. A stopwatch icon is faintly visible in the background, suggesting speed. Text overlay: \'2. Clear Call-to-Actions: Guiding Your Visitors\'\",\"A split screen. On one side, a website with a chaotic layout and tiny, unreadable text. On the other side, the same website with a clean, organized layout, ample white space, and large, readable fonts. Text overlay: \'3. Intuitive User Experience: Effortless Navigation\'\",\"A stylized bar graph showing increasing conversion rates with a magnifying glass icon hovering over it, emphasizing detail and optimization. A speech bubble with a question mark hovers over a user icon, then transitions to a satisfied user with a checkmark. Text overlay: \'4. Optimized Performance: Speed & SEO\' and \'