(125, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'instagram', 'Caption: brand awareness', 'Hey there, future homeowner/investor! 👋 Ever felt like finding your dream property in India was like searching for a needle in a haystack? 😩\n\nWell, say hello to Sabkhoj – your new best friend in the real estate world! 🏡 We\'re not just another property portal; we\'re here to make your journey smoother, smarter, and way more enjoyable. What makes us stand out? We\'re all about **transparency, detailed insights, and connecting you directly with trusted sellers and developers.** No more endless scrolling through outdated listings or guessing games! We bring you verified properties with all the info you need, right at your fingertips.\n\nReady to find your perfect place, without the stress? ✨\n\n**Start exploring sabkhoj.com today and discover a new way to real estate!**\n\n#Sabkhoj #RealEstateIndia #FindYourHome #PropertySearch #DreamHome #InvestInIndia #NewBeginnings #RealEstateMadeEasy #TransparentProperty #IndianRealEstate', 'draft', 1, 'Write a Casual & friendly Instagram caption for sabkhoj introducing the brand to tr. Highlight what makes sabkhoj unique in Real estate. Include a strong hook and CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: brand awareness\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 13:41:02', '2026-07-07 13:41:02'),
(126, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: product spotlight', 'Hey everyone! 👋 Ever wish you had a super-smart sidekick to help you find *exactly* what you\'re looking for, without all the endless scrolling? 🧐 Well, get ready to meet your new best friend!\n\nAt Sabkhoj, we\'re all about making your search simpler, smarter, and seriously satisfying. Our tech is designed to cut through the noise and deliver the most relevant results, saving you time and effort. Think less frustration, more \"aha!\" moments. ✨\n\nReady to experience a whole new way to search? Give Sabkhoj a try today and see the difference for yourself! 👇\n\n#Sabkhoj #SmartSearch #FindItFast #TechMadeEasy #ProductivityHacks #NewWayToSearch #TryItNow', 'draft', 1, 'Create a Casual & friendly caption for sabkhoj promoting teset. Target tr, focus on benefits, and end with a clear call to action.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: product spotlight\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 13:41:05', '2026-07-07 13:41:05'),
(127, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: engagement question', 'Hey Sabkhoj fam! 👋 Quick question for you all: What\'s the one thing you\'re testing out or trying to improve this week? Whether it\'s a new recipe, a workout routine, or even just a different way of organizing your thoughts – we want to know! Share your \"test\" with us in the comments below! 👇 Let\'s inspire each other to keep exploring and growing! Don\'t forget to tag a friend who\'s always up for a new challenge! #Sabkhoj #TestingNewThings #CommunityLove #ShareYourJourney #WhatsYourTest', 'draft', 1, 'Write an engaging Casual & friendly caption for sabkhoj that asks tr a question related to teset. Encourage comments and shares.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: engagement question\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 13:41:09', '2026-07-07 13:41:09'),
(128, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: educational tip', 'Hey there, SabKhoj fam! 👋 Ever wondered if you\'re getting the most out of your \"test for TR\" efforts? Here\'s a quick tip:\n\n**Focus on quality over quantity!** Instead of just running a ton of tests, take a moment to understand *why* each test is important and what specific insights you\'re hoping to gain. A well-thought-out, targeted test often yields far more valuable information than a dozen random ones. Happy testing! ✨\n\n#SabKhojTips #TestingTips #TRInsights #QualityOverQuantity #EdTech #LearningHacks', 'draft', 1, 'Draft a Casual & friendly educational caption for sabkhoj sharing a useful tip about teset for tr. Keep it concise and value-driven.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: educational tip\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 13:41:11', '2026-07-07 13:41:11'),
(129, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'x', 'Caption: promotional offer', 'Ready to find your dream home, TR? 🏡✨ The perfect property is out there, and with Sabkhoj, your search just got *way* easier and more exciting! We\'re talking about the best listings, all in one place, just for you. Don\'t let your dream home be someone else\'s reality – start exploring with Sabkhoj today! You won\'t believe what\'s waiting. 😉\n\n#Sabkhoj #RealEstateTR #DreamHome #PropertySearch #NewListing #HomeSweetHome #TRRealEstate #HouseHunting #FindYourHome #RealEstateGoals', 'draft', 1, 'Write a Casual & friendly promotional caption for sabkhoj with urgency and excitement. Target tr, mention teset, and include hashtags relevant to Real estate.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: promotional offer\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-07 13:41:14', '2026-07-07 13:41:14'),
