(155, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'facebook', 'SEO Best Practices', 'Boost your local Indian business visibility with these actionable SEO best practices! 🚀\n\nAre you a local Indian business struggling to get noticed online? Don\'t worry, Sabkhoj is here to help you shine! Here are 3 essential SEO tips you can implement today:\n\n1.  **Optimize your Google My Business (GMB) profile:** This is your digital storefront! Ensure all information is accurate, complete with high-quality photos, business hours, and customer reviews. Encourage happy customers to leave reviews – they\'re gold for local SEO!\n2.  **Target local keywords:** Think like your customers! What would they search for when looking for your products or services in your area? Use location-specific keywords in your website content, GMB profile, and social media posts (e.g., \"best *[your service]* in *[your city]*\").\n3.  **Build local citations and backlinks:** Get your business listed in local directories, industry-specific sites, and collaborate with other local businesses. These \"citations\" and \"backlinks\" tell Google you\'re a legitimate and relevant local player.\n\nImplementing these strategies can significantly improve your local search rankings and bring more customers through your doors (or to your website!).\n\nReady to take your local SEO to the next level? Sabkhoj specializes in helping Indian businesses dominate their local search results.\n\n👉 Want to know exactly where your business stands and how to improve? Get a FREE SEO audit from Sabkhoj today! Click here: [Link to your Free SEO Audit Page or relevant blog post on Sabkhoj website]\n\n#LocalSEO #IndianBusiness #SEOTips #DigitalMarketing #SmallBusinessIndia #GoogleMyBusiness #Sabkhoj #SEOExpert #GrowYourBusiness #LocalSearch', 'draft', 1, 'Create a Facebook post sharing 3-5 actionable SEO best practices for local Indian businesses. Position Sabkhoj as the expert in helping implement these strategies. Include a link to a relevant blog post on the Sabkhoj website if available, or a call to action for a free SEO audit.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"SEO Best Practices\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-09 14:44:31', '2026-07-09 14:44:31'),
