(157, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: product spotlight', '**Elevate Your Business in the Digital Age with Sabkhoj!** 🚀\n\nIn today\'s competitive Indian market, a robust online presence and strategic growth are non-negotiable. Sabkhoj is your trusted partner, offering a comprehensive suite of digital solutions designed to propel your business forward.\n\nFrom **Business Development** strategies that open new doors to cutting-edge **Android/IOS Development** that captivates your audience, we build the foundations for your success. Secure your online identity with reliable **Domain and Hosting**, and captivate visitors with stunning, user-friendly **Responsive Web Design**.\n\nDominate search results with expert **SEO** and targeted **Paid Search** campaigns, while our **Social Media Marketing** specialists craft engaging narratives that resonate. Need a clear roadmap? Our **Consulting** services provide invaluable insights. And with powerful **Lead Generation** and proactive **Brand Reputation Management**, we ensure your business not only grows but thrives with a sterling image.\n\n**Ready to unlock your full potential?** Visit sabkhoj.com today for a free consultation and let\'s build your digital success story together!\n\n#Sabkhoj #DigitalMarketingIndia #WebDevelopmentIndia #BusinessGrowth #SEOIndia #SocialMediaMarketingIndia #LeadGeneration #BrandManagement #AndroidDevelopment #IOSDevelopment #ResponsiveWebDesign #IndianBusiness #DigitalTransformation #GrowWithSabkhoj', 'draft', 1, 'Create a Professional & authoritative caption for sabkhojbrand promoting Sabkhoj offers a wide range of services including Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, Responsive Web Design, SEO, Paid Search, Social Media Marketing, Consulting, Lead Generation, and Brand Reputation Management.. Target Businesses in India seeking digital marketing, web development, and business growth solutions., focus on benefits, and end with a clear call to action.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: product spotlight\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-09 14:45:28', '2026-07-09 14:45:28'),
(158, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: engagement question', 'Tired of fragmented digital strategies holding your business back? 🚀 \n\nSabkhoj Brand offers a holistic suite of solutions designed to propel Indian businesses forward. From robust **Business Development** and cutting-edge **Android/iOS Development** to seamless **Domain & Hosting**, captivating **Responsive Web Design**, and powerful **SEO**, we\'ve got your digital presence covered. \n\nBut we don\'t stop there. Our expertise extends to impactful **Paid Search**, engaging **Social Media Marketing**, insightful **Consulting**, high-converting **Lead Generation**, and crucial **Brand Reputation Management**.\n\n**What\'s the *single biggest digital challenge* your Indian business faces right now in achieving its growth goals?** Share your insights below! Let\'s discuss how Sabkhoj can help you conquer it.\n\n#SabkhojBrand #DigitalMarketingIndia #BusinessGrowth #WebDevelopmentIndia #SEOIndia #LeadGeneration #BrandReputation #SMBIndia #IndianBusiness #DigitalTransformation', 'draft', 1, 'Write an engaging Professional & authoritative caption for sabkhojbrand that asks Businesses in India seeking digital marketing, web development, and business growth solutions. a question related to Sabkhoj offers a wide range of services including Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, Responsive Web Design, SEO, Paid Search, Social Media Marketing, Consulting, Lead Generation, and Brand Reputation Management.. Encourage comments and shares.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: engagement question\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-09 14:45:30', '2026-07-09 14:45:30'),
(159, 27, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'multi', 'Caption: educational tip', 'Unlock your business\'s full potential! 🚀 Did you know a cohesive digital strategy, from responsive web design to targeted SEO and lead generation, is crucial for Indian businesses aiming for significant growth? Sabkhoj provides end-to-end solutions to make it happen. #Sabkhoj #DigitalMarketing #BusinessGrowth #India #SEO #WebDevelopment #LeadGeneration #BrandManagement', 'draft', 1, 'Draft a Professional & authoritative educational caption for sabkhojbrand sharing a useful tip about Sabkhoj offers a wide range of services including Business Development, Android/IOS Development, Domain and Hosting, Responsive Web Design, SEO, Paid Search, Social Media Marketing, Consulting, Lead Generation, and Brand Reputation Management. for Businesses in India seeking digital marketing, web development, and business growth solutions.. Keep it concise and value-driven.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Caption: educational tip\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-09 14:45:32', '2026-07-09 14:45:32'),
(160, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'PPC Success Reel', 'You are an award-winning Creative Director, Cinematographer, Viral Instagram Reels Script Writer, and Brand Storytelling Expert.\r\n\r\nYour task is to create a highly engaging, cinematic, and viral Instagram Reel script for the following brand.\r\n\r\n## Brand Information\r\nBrand Name: [Brand Name]\r\nIndustry: [Industry]\r\nWebsite: [Website]\r\nTarget Audience: [Audience]\r\nGoal: [Lead Generation / Brand Awareness / Sales / Engagement]\r\nTone: [Professional / Luxury / Friendly / Bold / Premium]\r\nDuration: 30-45 seconds\r\n\r\n## Requirements\r\n\r\nCreate the reel using this exact structure:\r\n\r\n### 1. Hook (0-3 sec)\r\nCreate an attention-grabbing opening that stops scrolling immediately.\r\nMaximum 10 words.\r\n\r\n### 2. Problem (3-10 sec)\r\nShow the audience\'s biggest pain point.\r\n\r\n### 3. Solution (10-25 sec)\r\nIntroduce the brand naturally.\r\nExplain why it is different.\r\n\r\n### 4. Social Proof (25-35 sec)\r\nMention achievements, happy customers, ratings, awards, experience, or trust signals.\r\n\r\n### 5. CTA (35-45 sec)\r\nCreate a powerful call-to-action encouraging viewers to visit the website, send a DM, book a consultation, or contact the company.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nFor every scene provide:\r\n\r\nScene Number\r\n\r\nScene Duration\r\n\r\nVisual Description\r\n\r\nCamera Angle\r\n\r\nCamera Movement\r\n\r\nLighting\r\n\r\nBackground\r\n\r\nActor Expression\r\n\r\nAction\r\n\r\nText Overlay\r\n\r\nVoiceover\r\n\r\nSound Effects\r\n\r\nBackground Music\r\n\r\nTransition\r\n\r\nColor Grading\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nOutput in JSON format only.\r\n\r\n{\r\n\"title\":\"\",\r\n\"hook\":\"\",\r\n\"duration\":\"40 sec\",\r\n\"scenes\":[\r\n{\r\n\"scene\":1,\r\n\"duration\":\"0-3 sec\",\r\n\"visual\":\"\",\r\n\"camera_angle\":\"\",\r\n\"camera_movement\":\"\",\r\n\"lighting\":\"\",\r\n\"background\":\"\",\r\n\"actor\":\"\",\r\n\"action\":\"\",\r\n\"text_overlay\":\"\",\r\n\"voiceover\":\"\",\r\n\"sfx\":\"\",\r\n\"music\":\"\",\r\n\"transition\":\"\",\r\n\"color_grading\":\"\"\r\n}\r\n]\r\n}', 'draft', 1, 'Develop a 30-second Instagram Reel script showcasing a quick \'before and after\' scenario of a business\'s online visibility with and without Sabkhoj\'s PPC services. Use energetic music and text overlays. End with \'Boost your reach with Sabkhoj!\'', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"PPC Success Reel\",\"asset_id\":232,\"video_url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/aindracmo\\/public\\/app\\/brand\\/assets\\/232\",\"video_prompt\":\"Close-up of a frustrated small business owner staring at a blank computer screen, dim lighting, slow zoom out. Quick cut to a vibrant split-screen showing a bustling online store on one side and a thriving physical store on the other, bright, dynamic lighting, high-energy music. Text overlay: \\\"Boost your reach with Sabkhoj!\\\"\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/veo-3.1-lite\"}', NULL, '2026-07-11 04:58:56', '2026-07-11 11:28:05'),
(161, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'linkedin', 'SEO Benefits Post', 'Small business owners, listen up! 🚀 Ready to rocket your brand to the top? Investing in SEO isn\'t just an expense; it\'s your express ticket to explosive growth! Here are 3 undeniable benefits you\'re missing out on:\n\n1️⃣ **Dominate Search Results:** Stop hiding! SEO puts you front and center when customers are actively searching for what you offer. More visibility = more clicks = more customers!\n2️⃣ **Build Unshakeable Credibility:** High rankings signal trust and authority. When Google trusts you, your potential customers will too. Become the go-to expert in your niche!\n3️⃣ **Unlock Sustainable Growth:** Unlike paid ads, SEO brings in organic traffic that keeps flowing long after your initial investment. It\'s the gift that keeps on giving, building a robust customer pipeline for the long haul.\n\nDon\'t let your competitors steal your spotlight! It\'s time to invest in your online future.\n\nReady to see how Sabkhoj can transform your online presence? Visit our website today for a FREE consultation and let\'s chart your path to digital dominance! ➡️ [Your Website Link Here]\n\n#SEO #SmallBusiness #DigitalMarketing #GrowthHacking #Sabkhoj #BusinessGrowth #OnlineVisibility #FreeConsultation', 'draft', 1, 'Create a LinkedIn post highlighting 3 key benefits of investing in SEO for small businesses, using a bold and energetic tone. Include a call to action to visit Sabkhoj\'s website for a free consultation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"caption\",\"suggestion_title\":\"SEO Benefits Post\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/gemini-2.5-flash\"}', NULL, '2026-07-11 11:30:27', '2026-07-11 11:30:27'),
(162, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'post', 'x', 'Image: hero brand visual', 'A vibrant, photorealistic image of diverse small business owners (dentist, vet, cafe owner) smiling and interacting with a glowing, abstract digital interface, showcasing data and customer connections. Bold, energetic lighting, modern office/clinic backdrops. Overlay text: \"Sabkhojc: Grow Your Business.\"', 'draft', 1, 'Create an image post brief for sabkhojc: a clean hero visual showcasing the brand identity. Style: Bold & energetic. Audience: Small to medium-sized businesses across various industries, including specialized fields like dentistry and veterinary services, seeking to improve their digital presence and customer engagement.. Include layout, colors, and overlay text suggestions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"image\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Image: hero brand visual\",\"asset_id\":233,\"image_prompt\":\"A vibrant, photorealistic image of diverse small business owners (dentist, vet, cafe owner) smiling and interacting with a glowing, abstract digital interface, showcasing data and customer connections. Bold, energetic lighting, modern office\\/clinic backdrops. Overlay text: \\\"Sabkhojc: Grow Your Business.\\\"\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"black-forest-labs\\/flux.2-pro\"}', NULL, '2026-07-11 11:30:42', '2026-07-11 11:30:42'),
