(188, 33, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'reel_script', 'instagram', 'Reel: 3-second hook', 'Subject: A sleek, futuristic car, the DevFuser 45, glides effortlessly. Camera movement: Dynamic, following shot, then a slow, cinematic zoom on the car\'s emblem. Setting: A neon-lit cityscape at dusk. Lighting: Dramatic, with reflections of city lights on the car\'s polished surface. Mood: Sophisticated and aspirational.', 'draft', 1, 'Write a 30-second reel script for devfuser45 with a bold hook in the first 3 seconds. Topic: tdf. Tone: Professional & authoritative. Audience: gfd. Include scene directions and CTA.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"reel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Reel: 3-second hook\",\"asset_id\":306,\"video_url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/aindracmo\\/public\\/app\\/brand\\/assets\\/306\",\"video_prompt\":\"Subject: A sleek, futuristic car, the DevFuser 45, glides effortlessly. Camera movement: Dynamic, following shot, then a slow, cinematic zoom on the car\'s emblem. Setting: A neon-lit cityscape at dusk. Lighting: Dramatic, with reflections of city lights on the car\'s polished surface. Mood: Sophisticated and aspirational.\",\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"google\\/veo-3.1-lite\"}', NULL, '2026-07-14 14:14:29', '2026-07-14 14:14:29'),
(189, 33, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'carousel', 'instagram', 'Explaining \'tdf\' Service', 'A professional, clean, and modern image. The central focus is a bold title \'What is TDF?\' in a sans-serif font. Below, a brief, concise definition: \'TDF (Trusted Digital Framework) is a secure and interoperable digital identity and data sharing platform.\' The background is a subtle, abstract digital pattern, reminiscent of network connections, in shades of blue and grey, similar to the professional aesthetic of \'creative_1_linkedin.png\'.', 'draft', 1, 'Create an Instagram carousel post explaining what \'tdf\' is. Break down its key features and benefits across multiple slides, using the provided image \'creative_1_linkedin.png\' as inspiration for visual style. Maintain a professional and authoritative tone.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, '{\"from_content_suggestion\":true,\"suggestion_category\":\"carousel\",\"suggestion_title\":\"Explaining \'tdf\' Service\",\"carousel_group\":\"c5f3eb7a-313d-45f5-a11b-289dd8b855b0\",\"carousel_asset_ids\":[308,309,310,311],\"asset_id\":308,\"carousel_slide_prompts\":[\"A professional, clean, and modern image. The central focus is a bold title \'What is TDF?\' in a sans-serif font. Below, a brief, concise definition: \'TDF (Trusted Digital Framework) is a secure and interoperable digital identity and data sharing platform.\' The background is a subtle, abstract digital pattern, reminiscent of network connections, in shades of blue and grey, similar to the professional aesthetic of \'creative_1_linkedin.png\'.\",\"A professional, clean, and modern image highlighting \'Key Features\'. Three distinct icons, each representing a feature: 1. A shield with a checkmark (for Security), 2. Interlocking gears (for Interoperability), 3. A magnifying glass over data (for Data Control). Each icon is accompanied by a short, descriptive text: \'Enhanced Security\', \'Seamless Interoperability\', \'User-Centric Data Control\'. The background maintains the subtle digital pattern in blue\\/grey tones, consistent with \'creative_1_linkedin.png\'.\",\"A professional, clean, and modern image focusing on \'Benefits\'. Three distinct icons, each representing a benefit: 1. A person\'s silhouette with a padlock (for Trust), 2. Two hands shaking (for Collaboration), 3. A upward-trending arrow graph (for Efficiency). Each icon is accompanied by a short, descriptive text: \'Increased Trust\', \'Streamlined Collaboration\', \'Improved Operational Efficiency\'. The background maintains the subtle digital pattern in blue\\/grey tones, consistent with \'creative_1_linkedin.png\'.\",\"A professional, clean, and modern image with a call to action. The central element is a large, prominent text: \'Empowering Your Digital Future with TDF\'. Below, a smaller text: \'Learn more about how TDF can transform your digital interactions.\' A subtle button-like graphic with text \'Visit Our Website\' or \'Contact Us\' could be integrated without being an actual clickable button. The background is a slightly more pronounced, but still abstract, digital network pattern, in shades of blue and grey, maintaining the professional aesthetic of \'creative_1_linkedin.png\'.\"],\"ai_provider\":\"openrouter\",\"ai_model\":\"black-forest-labs\\/flux.2-pro\"}', NULL, '2026-07-14 14:15:26', '2026-07-14 14:15:26'),
